{
  "stem": "25348.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Anyhow, all of this, I told him that his daughter was a friend, his daughter [NON-ENGLISH]-- his name was-- her name was [NON-ENGLISH]-- that she was a friend of my brother's.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You looked for any connection.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She really was a friend of my brother's.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] You looked for any connection that could, you know, could be a, a linchpin in some relationships, in some contact.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, he said to me, put your finger in your mouth and throw up.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I wondered why he wanted to make me sick, you know, but then it dawned on me.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He said there are too many spies and too many eyes.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I can get you to Rovno.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] He didn't spell out partisan unit, but I knew.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He said but they-- that would take 10 days to a week.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He wanted that I pretended I had appendicitis.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] And before I could turn around, the nurses came and jabbed needles in to me.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I was operated on.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They took out my appendix, which I didn't know where it was.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] On the third day after that operation, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] his younger daughter came and threw my clothing onto the bed, took it out from the closet, and said, the police, they arrested my father.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They must not find you here.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Get out.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 10 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Where do I go?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] It was cold.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] As I was leaving, she said to me, [SOBBING] God be with you.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But God was on holiday.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He never looked in my direction.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I could hear shots within the hospital grounds.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
